        <% @page_title = "Alert Boxes" %>

        <h2><%= @page_title %></h2>
        <h5 class="subheader">An alert box is an element you can drop into a form or inline on a page to communicate success, warnings, failure or just information. They'll <a href="http://youtu.be/0lw17Pb7Nso" rel="nofollow">stretch</a> to 100% of the container width you put them in.</h5>

      </div>
    </div>

